Package: rpxl
Type: Package
Title: Read Password-Protected Excel Files
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Patrick", "Barks",
      email = "patrick.barks@epicentre.msf.org",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Uses the Python library msoffcrypto-tool to decrypt
    password-protected Excel files, which can then be read into R using readxl,
    readxlsb, or other packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    reticulate,
    readxl,
    readxlsb
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/epicentre-msf/rpxl
BugReports: https://github.com/epicentre-msf/rpxl/issues
